  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Frog Escape]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Background</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A frog girl, trapped in a secret underground lab, endured endless days of repetitive experiments. One day, she overheard a shocking conversation revealing her fate to be disposal. Determined not to wait any longer, she made up her mind to escape and seek freedom...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Frog Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to escape the lab, the frog girl must solve various puzzles. She can use her unique ability to cling to walls and ceilings to move. Use this ability to solve puzzles and advance towards your escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(However, be cautious, as she cannot cling to rough or uneven surfaces.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >P<strong>uzzle elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The maze-like laboratory is filled with various puzzle elements. One of the key features is the <u><strong>battery!</strong></u> Batteries can be obtained from <u><strong>battery storage units</strong></u> and have the advantage of being reusable multiple times. Utilize them to activate various devices in the lab and carve your way forward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Threats</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the frog girl moves forward, she will encounter various monsters and obstacles. The monsters will charge at her the moment they spot her. Can the frog girl overcome all these challenges and make her escape?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Frog Escape]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/012cfc18d32525e7d37fb1c34b6e797c.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Background</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A frog girl, trapped in a secret underground lab, endured endless days of repetitive experiments. One day, she overheard a shocking conversation revealing her fate to be disposal. Determined not to wait any longer, she made up her mind to escape and seek freedom...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/57fa239cf422fc21a09df5ba119ab1ba.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Frog Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to escape the lab, the frog girl must solve various puzzles. She can use her unique ability to cling to walls and ceilings to move. Use this ability to solve puzzles and advance towards your escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(However, be cautious, as she cannot cling to rough or uneven surfaces.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/d92cde1ffa47e0098dd4d346ce1dac66.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >P<strong>uzzle elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The maze-like laboratory is filled with various puzzle elements. One of the key features is the <u><strong>battery!</strong></u> Batteries can be obtained from <u><strong>battery storage units</strong></u> and have the advantage of being reusable multiple times. Utilize them to activate various devices in the lab and carve your way forward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/045a67b189c283c0f936ad0b83251f92.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.poster.avif?t=1739339114\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.webm?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344450/extras/8703f97ee3091f685e845ac2de90fd08.mp4?t=1739339114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Threats</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the frog girl moves forward, she will encounter various monsters and obstacles. The monsters will charge at her the moment they spot her. Can the frog girl overcome all these challenges and make her escape?</p>",
